      "span_text": "IL-4 variable number of tandem repeat (VNTR) was amplified through PCR based assay, using forward primer, 5'-TAGGCTGAAAGGGGGAAAGC-3 0 and reverse primer, 5'-CTGTTCACC TCAACTGCTCC-3'  ."
